{"tid":582492,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本宮崎和鹿兒島交界的新燃岳火山爆發。","createTime":"2018-03-06T08:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T10:24:58.000Z","uid":133522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6f11a7a07afc8feb58f2b555e4fd756a77baca9b","tid":582492,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 日本氣象廳發布消息指出，新燃岳火山今日下午發生爆發性噴發，是七年來首次的爆發性噴發，上次爆發在2011年1月。<br />\n<br />\n 新燃岳火山高1400多米，爆發後的火山濃煙升上距離火山口的2100米上空。"},{"pid":"610fe9a2c6da732c59d92142fec9c8b6c895e9d1","tid":582492,"uid":147238,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"已射 謝謝"},{"pid":"1d3f04f27fbc8acef02d47410489ee41fab50e66","tid":582492,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"過兩日去霧島，係唔係可以取消"},{"pid":"43389e245eb55e60c9b43432c5162dba563b7a88","tid":582492,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"唔想誤導你,留意下當地消息啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該無事嘅...可能比較多火山炭啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358f226300416083f7d6943c2e47c5c94dd02ed9","tid":582492,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"竟然係霧島"},{"pid":"6243599238b3929fddae1c9d1dcf318d600b87cc","tid":582492,"uid":86285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3f04f27fbc8acef02d47410489ee41fab50e66","tid":582492,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"過兩日去霧島，係唔係可以取消"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"今朝去霧島神宮都好多灰，咁啱走左就爆，你應該可以唔洗去了"},{"pid":"ec489659e891a95eb753c37bd08ce1e6a0931497","tid":582492,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:46:31.000Z","msg":"果到好似係行山熱點，附近又有個露營營地<im